<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 18:09:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>为什么以色列国防部长刚刚对内塔尼亚胡的加沙战争瘫痪打破沉默</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/why-israels-defense-minister-just-broke-his-silence-about-netanyahus-gaza-war-paralysis/0000018f-81fb-d720-a79f-abfbebf10000</link><description>以色列国防部长加兰特在新闻发布会上呼吁在加沙制定“事后计划”，这是他第三次公开批评内塔尼亚胡。虽然它不会让内塔尼亚胡垮台，但预示着更多的动荡</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 17:33:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/why-israels-defense-minister-just-broke-his-silence-about-netanyahus-gaza-war-paralysis/0000018f-81fb-d720-a79f-abfbebf10000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列心理健康危机的加剧，儿童和青少年精神科医生纷纷离开公共部门</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/as-mental-health-crisis-in-israel-grows-child-psychiatrists-leave-public-sector-in-droves/0000018f-81df-d720-a79f-abdf54270000</link><description>议会健康委员会提供的数据显示，尽管自 10 月 7 日以来儿童和青少年的心理健康问题有所增加，但需要心理健康专业人员的青少年可能需要等待八个月或更长时间才能得到治疗</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 17:17:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/as-mental-health-crisis-in-israel-grows-child-psychiatrists-leave-public-sector-in-droves/0000018f-81df-d720-a79f-abdf54270000</guid></item><item><title>新纳粹好奇心和以色列的捍卫者：侨民部长奇克利前往西班牙极右翼代表大会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/neo-nazi-curious-champions-of-israel-diaspora-minister-heads-to-spains-far-right-confab/0000018f-8192-d7f9-a5ff-b5f6d7fc0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡政府部长阿米哈伊·奇克利 (Amichai Chikli) 称匈牙利的欧尔班·维克多 (Viktor Orban) 为“一位杰出的领导人”，并参加了欧洲各地的一系列极右翼会议。欢迎新纳粹分子和大屠杀否认者加入其队伍</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 17:17:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/neo-nazi-curious-champions-of-israel-diaspora-minister-heads-to-spains-far-right-confab/0000018f-8192-d7f9-a5ff-b5f6d7fc0000</guid></item><item><title>“让美丽和恐怖发生在我身上：”10 月 7 日的以色列诗歌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/let-beauty-and-terror-happen-to-me-israeli-poems-on-october-7/0000018f-8122-d7f9-a5ff-b57627e60000</link><description>以色列诗人的作品被翻译成英语、法语、意大利语和西班牙语，收录在一本关于 10 月 7 日恐怖事件的新诗集中。另外，一个新的展览“预示”要求艺术家和参与者做到这一点，Etgar Keret出版第七部短篇小说集</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 17:09:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/let-beauty-and-terror-happen-to-me-israeli-poems-on-october-7/0000018f-8122-d7f9-a5ff-b57627e60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 223 天：阿拉伯联盟呼吁国际部队进驻加沙和约旦河西岸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-223-arab-league-calls-for-international-force-in-gaza-west-bank/0000018f-8234-d7f9-a5ff-b7767c470000</link><description>美国高级官员表示，美国与以色列国防部长加兰特一样担心以色列没有“战后”计划 ■ 加兰特表示，更多部队将加入以色列在拉法的行动 ■ 美国停泊临时浮动码头，向加沙海滩运送援助物资 ■ 以色列国防军正在进行调查以色列国防军坦克在加沙开火导致 5 名士兵死亡 ■ 真主党向以色列发射 40 枚火箭弹和爆炸性无人机 ■ 战争进入 223 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 17:05:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-223-arab-league-calls-for-international-force-in-gaza-west-bank/0000018f-8234-d7f9-a5ff-b7767c470000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵、国防部和军队无意中透露了加沙的部队集中情况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-troops-defense-ministry-and-army-unwittingly-reveal-troop-concentrations-in-gaza/0000018f-8203-d7f9-a5ff-b7772dcd0000</link><description>社交媒体上发布的加沙视频显示了确切位置并危及部队。至少一处地方有士兵受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 17:01:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-troops-defense-ministry-and-army-unwittingly-reveal-troop-concentrations-in-gaza/0000018f-8203-d7f9-a5ff-b7772dcd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在约旦河西岸被刺伤，伤势轻微；以色列国防军逮捕嫌疑人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-stabbed-in-west-bank-in-moderate-condition-idf-arrests-suspect/0000018f-8228-d430-a38f-c7ec74960000</link><description>该士兵在车内被刺伤，独立抵达附近一个军旅后被送往医院。经过三个小时的搜查，军方宣布在约旦河西岸的阿瓦尔塔村逮捕了一名嫌疑人</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 16:43:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-stabbed-in-west-bank-in-moderate-condition-idf-arrests-suspect/0000018f-8228-d430-a38f-c7ec74960000</guid></item><item><title>“必须阻止以色列”：南非结束国际法院辩论，呼吁以色列完全撤出加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/israel-must-be-stopped-s-africa-closes-icj-case-calls-for-full-withdrawal-from-gaza/0000018f-820d-dd4f-ab8f-97add0cb0000</link><description>国际法院听证会是在南非上周要求采取额外紧急措施以保护加沙南部拉法之后举行的。该国要求命令人道主义援助提供者不受阻碍地进入加沙，并补充说以色列迄今为止无视法院的命令</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 16:36:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/israel-must-be-stopped-s-africa-closes-icj-case-calls-for-full-withdrawal-from-gaza/0000018f-820d-dd4f-ab8f-97add0cb0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党火箭弹袭击以色列北部，三名士兵受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/three-soldiers-wounded-as-hezbollah-rocket-barrage-targets-northern-israel/0000018f-81fe-d9d6-a38f-85ff11d10000</link><description>无人机袭击以色列北部的一辆军车后，一名以色列士兵受重伤。真主党表示，这是对以色列对黎巴嫩境内发动的袭击的报复。以色列在黎巴嫩南部发动的袭击造成两人死亡</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 16:11:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/three-soldiers-wounded-as-hezbollah-rocket-barrage-targets-northern-israel/0000018f-81fe-d9d6-a38f-85ff11d10000</guid></item><item><title>新星节大屠杀幸存者穿着印有加沙人质肖像的连衣裙出席戛纳电影节</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/nova-festival-survivor-attends-cannes-film-festival-wearing-dress-with-hostages-portraits/0000018f-81a1-d7f9-a5ff-b5f7066a0000</link><description>10 月 7 日诺瓦节大屠杀中幸存的劳拉·布莱曼-卡达尔 (Laura Blajman-Kadar) 决定在戛纳红毯上让人们认识到仍在加沙被扣为人质的 132 名以色列人。 “我的裙子上印着我朋友的照片，这让我感到充满力量，我知道我这样做是为了他们”</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 14:51:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/nova-festival-survivor-attends-cannes-film-festival-wearing-dress-with-hostages-portraits/0000018f-81a1-d7f9-a5ff-b5f7066a0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，以色列人确信占领是不可避免的。事实恰恰相反</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/october-7-convinced-israelis-the-occupation-is-inevitable-the-opposite-is-true/0000018f-80da-d430-a38f-c5fe949a0000</link><description>与伊朗不同，西岸“哈马斯坦国”的风险不会威胁以色列的存在，也不会威胁以色列民主和全球支持的丧失</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 13:54:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/october-7-convinced-israelis-the-occupation-is-inevitable-the-opposite-is-true/0000018f-80da-d430-a38f-c5fe949a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列卡车开始从西岸向加沙运送人道主义援助物资</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-trucks-begin-transport-of-humanitarian-aid-into-gaza-from-the-west-bank/0000018f-8153-d430-a38f-c5f713960000</link><description>从约旦河西岸开往加沙的卡车数量有所增加，因为警方在国际法院就以色列在拉法的行动举行听证会之前开始采取措施，防止极右翼抗议者封锁和抢劫卡车</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 12:56:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-trucks-begin-transport-of-humanitarian-aid-into-gaza-from-the-west-bank/0000018f-8153-d430-a38f-c5f713960000</guid></item><item><title>随着新疾病和感染的蔓延，加沙的健康危机加剧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/health-crisis-in-gaza-spirals-as-new-diseases-infections-spread/0000018f-7d06-d7f9-a5ff-fd762e1e0000</link><description>数十万巴勒斯坦人遭受急性呼吸道感染和腹泻等问题，不干净的水和不卫生的条件加剧了人道主义局势的恶化。医疗非政府组织警告说，以色列对南部城市拉法的入侵使他们无法提供帮助</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 10:15:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/health-crisis-in-gaza-spirals-as-new-diseases-infections-spread/0000018f-7d06-d7f9-a5ff-fd762e1e0000</guid></item><item><title>五名以色列士兵在加沙北部被以色列国防军坦克炮火打死；三人重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/five-israeli-soldiers-killed-by-idf-tank-fire-in-northern-gaza-three-severely-wounded/0000018f-80a9-d7f9-a5ff-b5ffa8900000</link><description>初步调查显示，位于数十米外的以色列国防军坦克发现了武器，并向加沙北部贾巴利亚难民营的以色列国防军部队发射了炮弹</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 09:58:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/five-israeli-soldiers-killed-by-idf-tank-fire-in-northern-gaza-three-severely-wounded/0000018f-80a9-d7f9-a5ff-b5ffa8900000</guid></item><item><title>约旦河西岸以色列定居者袭击并打伤巴勒斯坦卡车司机，误以为他正在运送加沙援助物资</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settlers-wound-palestinian-truck-driver-falsely-assuming-he-was-hauling-gaza-aid/0000018f-8061-d7f9-a5ff-b577b8600000</link><description>极右翼活动分子在约旦河西岸拦截了多辆卡车，卸下货物，给轮胎放气并纵火焚烧。以色列警方抵达现场并没有逮捕任何嫌疑人</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 08:43:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settlers-wound-palestinian-truck-driver-falsely-assuming-he-was-hauling-gaza-aid/0000018f-8061-d7f9-a5ff-b577b8600000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列拘留期间死亡的加沙医生家人要求调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/family-of-gazan-doctor-who-died-in-israeli-custody-demand-judge-led-investigation/0000018f-803a-d9d6-a38f-85fbfef20001</link><description>Adnan Al-Bursh 医生现年 53 岁，是六个孩子的父亲，也是加沙市 Al-Shifa 医院骨科主任。他的妻子亚斯明 (Yasmin) 与以色列人权医生组织 (PHR) 的代表一起提交了请求</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 08:29:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/family-of-gazan-doctor-who-died-in-israeli-custody-demand-judge-led-investigation/0000018f-803a-d9d6-a38f-85fbfef20001</guid></item><item><title>国际法院就拉法军事入侵举行为期两天的听证会；以色列将于周五提出案件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/icj-opens-two-day-hearings-on-israels-military-incursion-into-rafah/0000018f-803f-d7f9-a5ff-b57f86dc0000</link><description>法律消息人士告诉《国土报》，以色列将辩称，在拉法的行动是针对哈马斯袭击和扣押人质的自卫行动的延续。以色列还将声称正在将巴勒斯坦平民转移到安全地点并向他们提供人道主义援助</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 07:27:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/icj-opens-two-day-hearings-on-israels-military-incursion-into-rafah/0000018f-803f-d7f9-a5ff-b57f86dc0000</guid></item><item><title>军方表示，美国将浮动码​​头停泊在加沙海滩，援助物资将在几天内送达</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/u-s-anchors-floating-pier-to-gaza-beach-aid-to-be-delivered-in-days-centcom-says/0000018f-8011-d430-a38f-c5f5d5aa0000</link><description>拜登于三月份宣布了该码头的建设，当时援助官员恳求以色列改善通过陆路进入加沙的救援物资的通道。美国希望通过开辟海上运送援助的路线来应对导致数十万人面临饥荒风险的人道主义危机</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 06:32:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/u-s-anchors-floating-pier-to-gaza-beach-aid-to-be-delivered-in-days-centcom-says/0000018f-8011-d430-a38f-c5f5d5aa0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列研究人员称，神秘的迦南石板原来是学校练习</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-05-16/ty-article/enigmatic-canaanite-tablet-turns-out-to-be-school-exercise-israeli-researchers-say/0000018f-7b85-df8f-a78f-ffdd85dd0000</link><description>近一个世纪前在贝丝谢梅什发现的铭文是由一位崭露头角的抄写员抄写的一系列字母，揭示了近 3,500 年前那里有一所学校的存在</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 06:03:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-05-16/ty-article/enigmatic-canaanite-tablet-turns-out-to-be-school-exercise-israeli-researchers-say/0000018f-7b85-df8f-a78f-ffdd85dd0000</guid></item><item><title>国防部长对内塔尼亚胡的可怕警告暴露了以色列领导层内部的深刻裂痕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/defense-chiefs-warning-to-netanyahu-highlights-the-growing-rift-in-israels-leadership/0000018f-7ddb-d604-af8f-7fdbf5fc0000</link><description>加兰特关于加沙“事后”的声明与甘茨和艾森科特震耳欲聋的沉默形成了鲜明对比——他们两人早就应该表态了。内塔尼亚胡像往常一样决定不做决定。这种公开的裂痕可能会增强哈马斯的信心，并使人质交易更加难以达成</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 03:00:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/defense-chiefs-warning-to-netanyahu-highlights-the-growing-rift-in-israels-leadership/0000018f-7ddb-d604-af8f-7fdbf5fc0000</guid></item></channel></rss>